OL,3,CHoyle says he cannot bring private
OL,4,Cprosecution in China spy case
OL,6,FMr Cash and Mr Berry ` who both deny
OL,7,Fwrongdoing ` were facing trial for
OL,8,Fallegedly passing information to
OL,9,FBeijing between 2021 and 2023, but the
OL,10,Fprosecution was discontinued in
OL,11,FSeptember.
OL,13,FSpeaking on BBC Radio 4's Week In
OL,14,FWestminster programme, Sir Lindsay
OL,15,Fsaid he did not "accept" the outcome
OL,16,Fand was still "very frustrated" after
OL,17,Fthe case collapsed.
