OL,3,CHoyle says he cannot bring private
OL,4,Cprosecution in China spy case
OL,6,F"I don't like it. I don't accept it.
OL,7,FSo much so, I wanted to know if I
OL,8,Fcould do a private prosecution. We've
OL,9,Ftaken top legal advice.
OL,11,F"My problem is there is no locus for
OL,12,Fme because everything I've tried, we
OL,13,Fjust can't get it there.
OL,15,F"But it doesn't stop us asking others
OL,16,Fwho may be able to take a private
OL,17,Fprosecution and what support can we
OL,18,Fgive them.
OL,20,F"It is a frustration, yes I'm angry,
OL,21,Fit must not happen again."
