OL,3,CHoyle says he cannot bring private
OL,4,Cprosecution in China spy case
OL,6,FSir Lindsay had previously said he was
OL,7,Fconsidering private action following
OL,8,Fthe decision to drop the charges,
OL,9,Fwhich he warned could leave Parliament
OL,10,Fvulnerable to espionage.
OL,12,FThe Crown Prosecution Service has said
OL,13,Fthe case could not progress because
OL,14,Fthe Government's deputy national
OL,15,Fsecurity adviser Matt Collins was
OL,16,Funwilling to classify China as an
OL,17,Factive threat to national security.
