OL,3,CHoyle says he cannot bring private
OL,4,Cprosecution in China spy case
OL,6,FMr Collins has said he had provided
OL,7,Fevidence of a "range of threats" posed
OL,8,Fby China but had not described the
OL,9,Fcountry as a "generic" threat because
OL,10,Fthat was not the position of the then-
OL,11,FTory government.
OL,13,FEarlier this week, the Attorney
OL,14,FGeneral blamed the collapse of case on
OL,15,F"out of date" UK espionage laws, which
OL,16,Fhe said were no longer "fit for
OL,17,Fpurpose".
