OL,3,CHoyle says he cannot bring private
OL,4,Cprosecution in China spy case
OL,6,FLord Richard Hermer said the use of
OL,7,Fthe term "enemy" in the Official
OL,8,FSecrets Act, which dates back to 1911,
OL,9,Fthrew up difficulties for prosecutors.
OL,11,FHe said the National Security Act 2023
OL,12,Fhad addressed this problem by
OL,13,Freplacing the word with a requirement
OL,14,Ffor prosecutors to prove merely that
OL,15,Finformation had been "passed to a
OL,16,Fforeign power".
