OL,3,CHoyle says he cannot bring private
OL,4,Cprosecution in China spy case
OL,6,FHe told Parliament's Joint Committee
OL,7,Fon the National Security Strategy
OL,8,F(JCNSS) on Wednesday: "Speaking
OL,9,Ffrankly, I don't understand why it
OL,10,Ftook Parliament so long to pass that.
OL,12,F"Had that Act been in force at the
OL,13,Frelevant time for this case, between
OL,14,F(2021-23), I have no doubt that the
OL,15,Fprosecution would have proceeded to
OL,16,Ftrial."
